summary: This is an email chain from November 2021 regarding an FBI 302 interview report of a witness. The email discusses adding the 302 to a production folder and mentions it is awaiting supervisor sign-off from the NYPD/FBI Child Exploitation Human Trafficking Task Force.

events.title: Email regarding 302 report status
events.description: An email exchange discusses the status of an FBI 302 interview report of a witness, noting it is awaiting supervisor sign-off from the NYPD/FBI Child Exploitation Human Trafficking Task Force.

keyFacts: The document is an email chain from November 2021 concerning an FBI 302 interview report.
The 302 report is related to a witness and is to be added to a production folder.
The report is from the NYPD/FBI Child Exploitation Human Trafficking Task Force and is awaiting supervisor sign-off.
The email notes the next day (November 12, 2021) is a holiday, which may delay the sign-off process.
